My boss invited my to lunch today and we ended up here. I've lived in Arizona most of my life and have driven past hundreds of times but never stopped.   Great bag lunch special for around $5 includes a selection of sausage with a variety of condiments, bag of chips and a can of soda. I went with the jalape√±o cheese and was not disappointed.   You can also stop by and pick up sausage and other meats by the pound. Potato and macaroni salads are also available. Best of all they have pierogi with a number of fillings.   If you haven't stopped, you're missing out.

